en.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E4%B8%89%E4%B9%98%E4%B8%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>道家丹经真伪杂陈，鱼目混珠，使读者不易辩认，即其修炼法诀，又不知何从。李道纯真人（宋末元初莹蟾子）将丹法分为三类：（一）（傍门九品）、（二）</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>三乘丹法</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>命功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>第一章 道可道，非常道；名可名，非常名。无名天地之始，有名万物之母。故常无欲，以观其妙；常有欲，以观其徼（jiào）。此两者同出而异名，同谓之</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经-马王堆帛书版</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</guid><description>01 道可道也，非恒道也。名可名也，非恒名也。无名万物之始也，有名万物之母也。故：恒无欲也，以观其眇；恒有欲也，以观其徼。两者同出，异名同谓。玄</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>《太乙金华宗旨》集要(最简)</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%99%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%AE%97%E6%97%A8%E9%9B%86%E8%A6%81/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%99%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%AE%97%E6%97%A8%E9%9B%86%E8%A6%81/</guid><description>一、实修功法 概要： 1、回光之功，全用逆法，注想天心，天心居曰月中。 2、诸子只去回光，便是无上妙谛。光易动而难定，回之既久，此光凝结，即是自然</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>太乙金华宗旨</category><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>命功</category><category>摘要</category><category>道</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>《青华秘文》丹诀钩玄</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87%E4%B8%B9%E8%AF%80%E9%92%A9%E7%8E%84/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87%E4%B8%B9%E8%AF%80%E9%92%A9%E7%8E%84/</guid><description>中孚子按语 世传张伯端真人三传匪人三受天谴，何以竟著《悟真篇》以丹道公开度世耶？盖丹家每言有道不传谓之“闭天道”，传予匪人谓之“泄天机”，皆七</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>青华秘文</category><category>张伯端</category><category>紫阳真人</category><category>命功</category><category>摘要</category><category>道</category><category>南宗</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>太上升玄消灾护命妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%8E%84%E6%B6%88%E7%81%BE%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%BD%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%8E%84%E6%B6%88%E7%81%BE%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%BD%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>尔时，元始天尊在七宝林中，五明宫内，与无极圣众，俱放无极光明，照无极世界，观无极众生，受无极苦恼；宛转世间，轮回生死，漂浪爱河，流吹欲海，沉</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>消灾护命妙经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上灵宝天尊说禳灾度厄经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E7%81%B5%E5%AE%9D%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%8A%E8%AF%B4%E7%A6%B3%E7%81%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%8E%84%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E7%81%B5%E5%AE%9D%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%8A%E8%AF%B4%E7%A6%B3%E7%81%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%8E%84%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>尔时天尊在禅黎国土，与大道真仙万万亿千人，诸天尊及诸天龙鬼神，尽来集会，受吾约束。世间若有善男子善女人，忽有年灾月厄，游城赤鼠之厄，天罗地网</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>禳灾度厄经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上老君说常清静妙经篡图解注王玠</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F%E5%9B%BE%E8%A7%A3%E6%B3%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F%E5%9B%BE%E8%A7%A3%E6%B3%A8/</guid><description>版本是元末道士王玠所注解，王玠，字道渊，号混然子。有自述小令《混然歌》： 混然道士何所为，三家村里藏踪迹。 无去无来每独存，无形无名赤厉历。 一点</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>讲经</category></item><item><title>太上老君说常清静经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>老君曰：大道无形，生育天地；大道无情，运行日月；大道无名，长养万物；吾不知其名，强名曰道。夫道者：有清有浊，有动有静；天清地浊，天动地静；男</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>性功</category><category>早晚课</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太乙金华宗旨-道藏续编</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%99%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%AE%97%E6%97%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%99%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%AE%97%E6%97%A8/</guid><description>金华宗旨序 道在目前，身体自得，何劳身外寻求哉。人身为三才合一之身，造物赋我，其用甚大。我人日具而不知，圣人悯之，征诸一身以示之。盖谓道在一身</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>太乙金华宗旨</category><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>命功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>永嘉大师证道歌</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B0%B8%E5%98%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%E8%AF%81%E9%81%93%E6%AD%8C/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B0%B8%E5%98%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%E8%AF%81%E9%81%93%E6%AD%8C/</guid><description>有四种注释，现在和并在一起，比较对照，加深印象。今后每天会有一段文字，节录这些注释。我从开始学佛就接触到永嘉证道歌，当时还希望自己能够背诵。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>证道歌</category><category>佛</category><category>禅宗</category></item><item><title>洞玄灵宝定观经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>诵读 天尊告左玄真人曰：夫欲修道，先能舍事。 外事都绝，无与忤心。然后安坐，内观心起。若觉一念起，须除灭, 务令安静。 其次，虽非的有贪着，浮游乱想</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>定观经</category><category>性功</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道家早課(繁体)</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%97%A9%E8%AF%BE-%E7%B9%81%E4%BD%93/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%97%A9%E8%AF%BE-%E7%B9%81%E4%BD%93/</guid><description>太上玄門日誦早晚課 玄門日誦早課 上壇行教一體同觀 依上和音功德無量 澄清韻 琳琅振響。十方肅清。河海靜默。山嶽吞雲。萬靈鎮伏。招集群仙。 天無氛穢。地</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>早课</category><category>繁体</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道家晚課(繁体)</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%99%9A%E8%AF%BE-%E7%B9%81%E4%BD%93/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%99%9A%E8%AF%BE-%E7%B9%81%E4%BD%93/</guid><description>太上玄門日誦早晚課 玄門日誦晚課 步虛韻 大道洞玄虛。有念無不契。錬質入仙真。遂成金剛體。 超度三界難。地獄五苦解。悉皈 太上經。靜念稽首禮。 太上度人</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>晚课</category><category>繁体</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道教神咒</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%92/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%92/</guid><description>净心神咒 太上台星，应变无停。 驱邪缚魅，保命护身。 智慧明净，心神安宁。 三魂永久，魄无丧倾。 急急如律令。 净口神咒 丹朱口神，吐秽除氛。舌神正伦，通</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道</category><category>咒</category></item><item><title>金花的秘密</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86/</guid><description>译者按：《太乙金华宗旨》共有十三章，卫礼贤只翻译了前八章，且有个别段落没有译出来，后面五章卫礼贤觉得价值没有那么大而未译出。《慧命经》全书共</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>金花的秘密</category><category>太乙金华宗旨</category><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>命功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>青华秘文</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87/</guid><description>玉清金笥青华秘文金宝内炼丹诀 紫阳真人张伯端撰 远师真人王邦叔授 东和希古渔人刘元一受 序 远师真人王邦叔，不知何许人也。时年十九，侍紫阳真人为弟子。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>青华秘文</category><category>张伯端</category><category>紫阳真人</category><category>命功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>南宗</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>高上玉皇心印妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上药三品，神与气精，恍恍惚惚，杳杳冥冥. 存无守有，顷刻而成，回风混合，百日功灵。 默朝上帝，一纪飞升，智者易悟，昧者难行。 履践天光，呼吸育清，</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心印妙经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>命功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄帝阴符经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上篇 观天之道，执天之行，尽矣。故天有五贼，见之者昌。五贼在心，施行于天。宇宙在乎手，万化生乎身。天性，人也；人心，机也。立天之道，以定人也。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄帝阴符经</category><category>阴符经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭中景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>念吾头顶戴天神 发为星辰万余纶 纡长槃屈光若玄 顶上中央名通天 孔德之容大如钱 天星和气从此间 养人骨髓浸灵根 下和六府绍五宫 消除恶气出脐门 还念两目白黑分</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭中景经</category><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭内景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%86%85%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%86%85%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上清章第一 上清紫霞虚皇前，太上大道玉晨君。闲居蕊珠作七言，散化五形变万神。 是为黄庭曰内篇，琴心三叠舞胎仙。九气映明出霄间，神盖童子生紫烟。 是</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭内景经</category><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭外景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%96%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%96%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上部经第一 老君闲居作七言，解说身形及诸神。上有黄庭下关元，后有幽阙前命门。 呼吸庐间入丹田，玉池清水灌灵根。审能修之可长存，黄庭中人衣朱衣。 关</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭外景经</category><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item></channel></rss>